SUMMARY:Deadline: Cohere Labs Scholars Program 2026 (2027 cohort)
DESCRIPTION:Cohere Labs Scholars Program\, a paid full-time research appren
 ticeship for emerging machine-learning researchers\, explicitly aimed at n
 on-traditional entrants to the field. ELIGIBILITY: emerging ML researchers
 \; no PhD or prior publication required\; open worldwide\, remote-first. A
 pply via the Cohere Labs Scholars Program page.\n\nOrganisation: Cohere La
 bs (formerly Cohere For AI)\nLocation: Remote-first (worldwide)\nAward: Fu
 ll-time paid eight-month research apprenticeship with a weekly stipend and
  health benefits (equivalent roughly $103\,000 to $163\,000/year). No appl
 ication fee.\nDuration: Eight months full-time (January to August 2027 coh
 ort)\n\nMore: https://cohere.com/research/scholars-program
URL:https://cohere.com/research/scholars-program
LOCATION:Remote-first (worldwide)
